-- ASB Bank Becomes First on Facebook to Offer Financial Service, Herald Says
-- B y   C h r i s   B o u r k e
-- 2010-11-16T20:38:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-16/asb-bank-becomes-first-on-facebook-to-offer-financial-service-herald-says.html
ASB Bank Ltd. has become the first
financial services company in the world to offer banking
services on Facebook, the New Zealand Herald reported today.  The bank has created a “virtual branch” on the social
networking website that allows its customers to discuss their
accounts with ASB staff, the  Auckland-based paper  reported,
citing a bank spokeswoman. Around 13,000 people have downloaded
an application for the site, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
